com.avionos.aem.foundation.api.page

Interface FoundationPage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Accessible, Adaptable, Inheritable, com.day.cq.commons.LabeledResource, Linkable, com.day.cq.wcm.api.Page, Traversable<FoundationPage>

    public interface FoundationPage
extends com.day.cq.wcm.api.Page, Accessible, Inheritable, Linkable, Traversable<FoundationPage>
    Decorates the Page interface with additional convenience methods for traversing the content hierarchy and getters for Avionos AEM Foundation classes.

      • getAbsoluteParent

        FoundationPage getAbsoluteParent(int level)
        Returns the absolute parent page. If no page exists at that level, null is returned.

        Example (this path == /content/geometrixx/en/products) 

         | level | returned                        |
 |     0 | /content                        |
 |     1 | /content/geometrixx             |
 |     2 | /content/geometrixx/en          |
 |     3 | /content/geometrixx/en/products |
 |     4 | null                            |
        Specified by:
        getAbsoluteParent in interface com.day.cq.wcm.api.Page
        Parameters:
        level - hierarchy level of the parent page to retrieve
        Returns:
        the respective parent page or null
